(9, 'LYING DOWN/OCCUPYING MORE THAN ONE SEAT 1050.7 (J)', 'AT T/P/O P.O. OBSERVED RESP. LYING DOWN (STATE STATIONAREA) SUBWAY SYSTEM BLOCKING PEDESTRIAN FLOW OF TRAFFIC<br><br>AT T/P/O P.O. OBSERVED RESP LYING DOWN AND OCCUPYING MORE THAN ONE SEAT ON /B.TRAIN<br><br>AT T/P/O P.O. OBSERVED RESP OCCUPYING MORE THAN ONESEATON _/B _TRAIN AND DENIED OTHER PASSENGERS AN ENTITLED SEAT.<br><br>'),
