(11, 'UNAUTHORIZED SOUND PRODUCTION DEVICE (RADIO) 1050.7(E) - $50.00', 'AT T/P/O P.O. OBSERVED RESP. PLAYING RADIO ON TRAIN WHICH WAS AUDIBLE TO OTHERPASSENGERS IN SUBWAY SYSTEM.<br>'),
